snippet.title: This Never Happened
snippet.description:
Rather than pander to the purists or create music for DJs alone, Daniel Goldstein aka Lane 8 has always tread his own, distinctive path - perhaps best summed up by his phones-free event concept and label This Never Happened. 

In tandem with the events, Daniel’s output on the TNH label has stood out for its integrity and artistry whether on emotional epics like ‘Fingerprint’ or quirky upbeat groovers such as ‘Run’. Always defined by a melodic touch, TNH is the culmination of a steady, assured rise over recent years.
